markets.rules_primary: If the yield curve par rate for 10-year U.S. treasury notes is between 3.64-3.66 % on May 22, 2023, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The market will expire at the sooner of the first 7:00 PM ET following the data release for May 22, 2023, or one week following May 22, 2023.
